{"type":"message","id":"3a1d0cfb","parentId":"1796063d","timestamp":"2026-03-05T03:48:13.546Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我看到了有 start-proxy.ps1 和 stop-proxy.ps1 脚本。让我查看这些脚本的内容，了解如何启动和停止服务，然后创建守护进程监控脚本。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a95f96161c8e46e698d88874","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"G:\\openClaw\\xiaoxia\\skills\\codex-cn-bridge\\scripts\\start-proxy.ps1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e7b40ea48a1a4eb9823c287e","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"G:\\openClaw\\xiaoxia\\skills\\codex-cn-bridge\\scripts\\stop-proxy.ps1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":21093,"output":172,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21265,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772682489588}}
{"type":"message","id":"63b4e400","parentId":"3a1d0cfb","timestamp":"2026-03-05T03:48:13.562Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a95f96161c8e46e698d88874","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Codex CN Bridge - Start Proxy Service\n# Usage: /codex-cn-bridge start\n\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\n$OutputEncoding = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8\n[Console]::OutputEncoding = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8\n\n$SkillDir = Split-Path -Parent $MyInvocation.MyCommand.Path\n$SkillDir = Split-Path -Parent $SkillDir\n$ProxyDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.codex\\cn-bridge\"\n\nWrite-Host \"============================================\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"  Codex CN Bridge - Protocol Converter\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"  Use Domestic AI Models with Codex\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"============================================\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# Check config directory\nif (-not (Test-Path $ProxyDir)) {\n    Write-Host \"[*] Creating config directory...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    New-Item -ItemType Directory -Force -Path $ProxyDir | Out-Null\n}\n\n# Check .env file\n$EnvFile = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.codex\\cn-bridge.env\"\nif (-not (Test-Path $EnvFile)) {\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"[!] Config file not found: $EnvFile\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"Please configure API Key (choose one):\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"  Method 1: Create .env file\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n    Write-Host \"  $EnvFile\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n    Write-Host \"  Content:\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n    Write-Host \"  QWEN_API_KEY=sk-your-alibaba-cloud-key\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"  Method 2: Set environment variable\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n    Write-Host \"  [System.Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable('QWEN_API_KEY', 'sk-your-key', 'User')\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    exit 1\n}\n\n# Check Python\ntry {\n    $PythonCmd = Get-Command python -ErrorAction Stop\n    Write-Host \"[OK] Python installed: $($PythonCmd.Source)\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"[!] Python not found, please install Python 3.8+\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    exit 1\n}\n\n# Check dependencies\nWrite-Host \"[*] Checking dependencies...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\ntry {\n    python -c \"import fastapi, uvicorn, httpx, yaml, dotenv\" 2>$null\n    if ($LASTEXITCODE -ne 0) {\n        throw \"Missing packages\"\n    }\n    Write-Host \"[OK] Dependencies installed\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"[*] Installing dependencies...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    pip install fastapi uvicorn httpx pyyaml python-dotenv -q\n    Write-Host \"[OK] Dependencies installed\" -ForegroundColor Green\n}\n\n# Deploy proxy script to config directory\nWrite-Host \"[*] Deploying proxy service...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nCopy-Item \"$SkillDir\\src\\proxy.py\" \"$ProxyDir\\proxy.py\" -Force\nCopy-Item \"$SkillDir\\config\\models.yaml\" \"$ProxyDir\\models.yaml\" -Force\n\n# Check port usage\n$Port = 3000\n$ExistingProcess = Get-NetTCPConnection -LocalPort $Port -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($ExistingProcess) {\n    Write-Host \"[!] Port $Port already in use (PID: $($ExistingProcess.OwningProcess))\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    Write-Host \"    Run '/codex-cn-bridge stop' to stop old process\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    exit 1\n}\n\n# Load environment variables\nWrite-Host \"[*] Loading environment variables...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nif (Test-Path $EnvFile) {\n    Get-Content $EnvFile | ForEach-Object {\n        if ($_ -notmatch \"^#\" -and $_ -match \"=\") {\n            $key, $value = $_.Split(\"=\", 2)\n            [System.Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable($key.Trim(), $value.Trim(), \"Process\")\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n# Start service\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"[OK] Starting proxy service...\" -ForegroundColor Green\nWrite-Host \"    Listening: http://localhost:$Port\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"    Config: $EnvFile\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"Press Ctrl+C to stop service\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\nSet-Location $ProxyDir\npython proxy.py\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772682493557}}
{"type":"message","id":"c10af9b0","parentId":"63b4e400","timestamp":"2026-03-05T03:48:13.576Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e7b40ea48a1a4eb9823c287e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Codex CN Bridge - 停止代理服务\n# 用法：/codex-cn-bridge stop\n\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"SilentlyContinue\"\n\nWrite-Host \"============================================\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"  Codex CN Bridge - 停止服务\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"============================================\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# 查找并停止进程\n$Port = 3000\n$Process = Get-NetTCPConnection -LocalPort $Port -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object -ExpandProperty OwningProcess -Unique\n\nif ($Process) {\n    Write-Host \"[?] 找到运行中的服务 (PID: $Process)\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    \n    foreach ($Pid in $Process) {\n        try {\n            $ProcInfo = Get-Process -Id $Pid -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n            if ($ProcInfo -and $ProcInfo.ProcessName -eq \"python\") {\n                Write-Host \"[?] 停止进程 $Pid ($($ProcInfo.ProcessName))...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n                Stop-Process -Id $Pid -Force\n                Write-Host \"[✓] 已停止\" -ForegroundColor Green\n            }\n        } catch {\n            Write-Host \"[!] 无法停止进程 $Pid : $_\" -ForegroundColor Red\n        }\n    }\n    \n    # 等待端口释放\n    Start-Sleep -Seconds 2\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"[✓] 服务已停止\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"[i] 未发现运行中的服务\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"提示：运行 '/codex-cn-bridge start' 重新启动服务\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772682493571}}
{"type":"message","id":"acc42ec2","parentId":"c10af9b0","timestamp":"2026-03-05T03:48:41.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我现在了解了服务的启动和停止方式。现在我需要创建一个守护进程脚本来监控 qwen-proxy 服务。这个守护进程需要：\n\n1. 监控端口 3000 是否有服务在监听\n2. 服务停止时自动重启\n3. 定期检查服务健康状态\n4. 异常时主动汇报\n\n让我创建一个 PowerShell 守护进程脚本。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在我创建守护进程监控脚本：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f20315a6e58f447bbda25a20","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"G:\\openClaw\\xiaoxia\\skills\\codex-cn-bridge\\scripts\\watchdog.ps1","content":"# Codex CN Bridge - 守护进程监控脚本\n# 功能：监控 qwen-proxy 服务状态，自动重启，健康检查，异常汇报\n# 用法：.\\watchdog.ps1 或作为后台任务运行\n\nparam(\n    [int]$CheckInterval = 30,      # 检查间隔（秒）\n    [int]$HealthCheckInterval = 300, # 健康检查间隔（秒）\n    [string]$LogPath = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.codex\\cn-bridge\\watchdog.log\",\n    [switch]$AsBackground         # 是否作为后台任务运行\n)\n\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Continue\"\n$Port = 3000\n$ServiceName = \"qwen-proxy\"\n$StartTime = Get-Date\n\n# 确保日志目录存在\n$LogDir = Split-Path -Parent $LogPath\nif (-not (Test-Path $LogDir)) {\n    New-Item -ItemType Directory -Force -Path $LogDir | Out-Null\n}\n\n# 日志函数\nfunction Write-Log {\n    param(\n        [string]$Message,\n        [string]$Level = \"INFO\"\n    )\n    $Timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\"\n    $LogEntry = \"[$Timestamp] [$Level] $Message\"\n    \n    # 控制台输出\n    switch ($Level) {\n        \"INFO\" { Write-Host $LogEntry -ForegroundColor Green }\n        \"WARN\" { Write-Host $LogEntry -ForegroundColor Yellow }\n        \"ERROR\" { Write-Host $LogEntry -ForegroundColor Red }\n        \"HEALTH\" { Write-Host $LogEntry -ForegroundColor Cyan }\n    }\n    \n    # 写入日志文件\n    Add-Content -Path $LogPath -Value $LogEntry -Encoding UTF8\n}\n\n# 检查服务是否在运行\nfunction Test-ServiceRunning {\n    try {\n        $Connection = Get-NetTCPConnection -LocalPort $Port -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n        if ($Connection) {\n            $Pid = $Connection.OwningProcess | Select-Object -First 1\n            $Process = Get-Process -Id $Pid -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n            if ($Process) {\n                return @{\n                    Running = $true\n                    Pid = $Pid\n                    ProcessName = $Process.ProcessName\n                    StartTime = $Process.StartTime\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        return @{ Running = $false }\n    } catch {\n        return @{ Running = $false }\n    }\n}\n\n# 启动服务\nfunction Start-ProxyService {\n    Write-Log \"正在启动 $ServiceName 服务...\" \"INFO\"\n    \n    $ProxyDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.codex\\cn-bridge\"\n    $EnvFile = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.codex\\cn-bridge.env\"\n    $SkillDir = \"G:\\openClaw\\xiaoxia\\skills\\codex-cn-bridge\"\n    \n    # 检查配置文件\n    if (-not (Test-Path $EnvFile)) {\n        Write-Log \"配置文件不存在：$EnvFile\" \"ERROR\"\n        return $false\n    }\n    \n    # 检查 Python\n    try {\n        $PythonCmd = Get-Command python -ErrorAction Stop\n    } catch {\n        Write-Log \"未找到 Python，请安装 Python 3.8+\" \"ERROR\"\n        return $false\n    }\n    \n    # 部署 proxy.py\n    if (Test-Path \"$SkillDir\\src\\proxy.py\") {\n        Copy-Item \"$SkillDir\\src\\proxy.py\" \"$ProxyDir\\proxy.py\" -Force\n        Copy-Item \"$SkillDir\\config\\models.yaml\" \"$ProxyDir\\models.yaml\" -Force\n    }\n    \n    # 启动服务（后台运行）\n    $StartInfo = New-Object System.Diagnostics.ProcessStartInfo\n    $StartInfo.FileName = \"python\"\n    $StartInfo.Arguments = \"proxy.py\"\n    $StartInfo.WorkingDirectory = $ProxyDir\n    $StartInfo.RedirectStandardOutput = $true\n    $StartInfo.RedirectStandardError = $true\n    $StartInfo.UseShellExecute = $false\n    $StartInfo.CreateNoWindow = $true\n    \n    # 加载环境变量\n    if (Test-Path $EnvFile) {\n        Get-Content $EnvFile | ForEach-Object {\n            if ($_ -notmatch \"^#\" -and $_ -match \"=\") {\n                $key, $value = $_.Split(\"=\", 2)\n                $StartInfo.EnvironmentVariables[$key.Trim()] = $value.Trim()\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    \n    $Process = New-Object System.Diagnostics.Process\n    $Process.StartInfo = $StartInfo\n    \n    try {\n        $Process.Start() | Out-Null\n        Start-Sleep -Seconds 3\n        \n        # 验证服务是否启动成功\n        $Status = Test-ServiceRunning\n        if ($Status.Running) {\n            Write-Log \"$ServiceName 服务已启动 (PID: $($Status.Pid))\" \"INFO\"\n            return $true\n        } else {\n            Write-Log \"服务启动失败\" \"ERROR\"\n            return $false\n        }\n    } catch {\n        Write-Log \"启动服务时出错：$_\" \"ERROR\"\n        return $false\n    }\n}\n\n# 停止服务\nfunction Stop-ProxyService {\n    Write-Log \"正在停止 $ServiceName 服务...\" \"INFO\"\n    \n    $Status = Test-ServiceRunning\n    if ($Status.Running) {\n        try {\n            Stop-Process -Id $Status.Pid -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n            Start-Sleep -Seconds 2\n            Write-Log \"服务已停止\" \"INFO\"\n            return $true\n        } catch {\n            Write-Log \"停止服务失败：$_\" \"ERROR\"\n            return $false\n        }\n    }\n    return $true\n}\n\n# 健康检查\nfunction Invoke-HealthCheck {\n    Write-Log \"执行健康检查...\" \"HEALTH\"\n    \n    try {\n        $Response = Invoke-WebRequest -Uri \"http://localhost:$Port/\" -TimeoutSec 5 -UseBasicParsing -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n        if ($Response.StatusCode -eq 200) {\n            Write-Log \"健康检查通过 - 服务响应正常\" \"HEALTH\"\n            return $true\n        } else {\n            Write-Log \"健康检查失败 - 状态码：$($Response.StatusCode)\" \"WARN\"\n            return $false\n        }\n    } catch {\n        Write-Log \"健康检查失败 - 服务无响应：$_\" \"ERROR\"\n        return $false\n    }\n}\n\n# 发送异常通知（可扩展）\nfunction Send-Alert {\n    param(\n        [string]$Message\n    )\n    Write-Log \"⚠️ 异常警报：$Message\" \"ERROR\"\n    # 这里可以集成通知渠道（如钉钉、企业微信、邮件等）\n    # 示例：发送钉钉通知\n    # $WebhookUrl = \"https://oapi.dingtalk.com/robot/send?access_token=xxx\"\n    # $Body = @{ msgtype = \"text\"; text = @{ content = $Message } } | ConvertTo-Json\n    # Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $WebhookUrl -Method Post -Body $Body -ContentType \"application/json\"\n}\n\n# 主监控循环\nfunction Start-Watchdog {\n    Write-Log \"============================================\" \"INFO\"\n    Write-Log \"  $ServiceName 守护进程已启动\" \"INFO\"\n    Write-Log \"  端口：$Port\" \"INFO\"\n    Write-Log \"  检查间隔：$CheckInterval 秒\" \"INFO\"\n    Write-Log \"  健康检查间隔：$HealthCheckInterval 秒\" \"INFO\"\n    Write-Log \"  日志路径：$LogPath\" \"INFO\"\n    Write-Log \"============================================\" \"INFO\"\n    Write-Log \"\"\n    \n    $LastHealthCheck = Get-Date\n    $RestartCount = 0\n    $LastRestartTime = $null\n    \n    while ($true) {\n        try {\n            # 检查服务状态\n            $Status = Test-ServiceRunning\n            \n            if (-not $Status.Running) {\n                Write-Log \"服务未运行，尝试重启...\" \"WARN\"\n                Send-Alert \"$ServiceName 服务异常停止，正在重启\"\n                \n                $RestartCount++\n                $LastRestartTime = Get-Date\n                \n                if (Start-ProxyService) {\n                    Write-Log \"服务重启成功\" \"INFO\"\n                } else {\n                    Write-Log \"服务重启失败，将在下次循环重试\" \"ERROR\"\n                    Send-Alert \"$ServiceName 服务重启失败\"\n                }\n            } else {\n                # 定期检查健康状态\n                $TimeSinceLastHealthCheck = (Get-Date) - $LastHealthCheck\n                if ($TimeSinceLastHealthCheck.TotalSeconds -ge $HealthCheckInterval) {\n                    $HealthStatus = Invoke-HealthCheck\n                    $LastHealthCheck = Get-Date\n                    \n                    if (-not $HealthStatus) {\n                        Write-Log \"健康检查失败，尝试重启服务...\" \"WARN\"\n                        Stop-ProxyService\n                        Start-Sleep -Seconds 3\n                        Start-ProxyService\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n            \n            # 等待下次检查\n            Start-Sleep -Seconds $CheckInterval\n            \n        } catch {\n            Write-Log \"监控循环出错：$_\" \"ERROR\"\n            Start-Sleep -Seconds 10\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n# 启动守护进程\nStart-Watchdog\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":22642,"output":2386,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25028,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772682493577}}
