{"type":"message","id":"272d423f","parentId":"501ada81","timestamp":"2026-03-05T03:53:11.163Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"端口已释放。现在让我修复 watchdog 脚本中的服务检测逻辑，使用更可靠的方法。问题可能是 Get-NetTCPConnection 在某些 PowerShell 会话中行为不同。\n\n让我更新 watchdog 脚本，使用更 robust 的检测方法：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在修复 watchdog 脚本，使用更可靠的服务检测：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6575500bb5594e5aa940bddd","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"G:\\openClaw\\xiaoxia\\skills\\codex-cn-bridge\\scripts\\watchdog.ps1","oldText":"# Check if service is running\nfunction Test-ServiceRunning {\n    try {\n        $Connection = Get-NetTCPConnection -LocalPort $Port -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n        if ($Connection) {\n            $Pid = $Connection.OwningProcess | Select-Object -First 1\n            $Process = Get-Process -Id $Pid -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n            if ($Process) {\n                return @{\n                    Running = $true\n                    Pid = $Pid\n                    ProcessName = $Process.ProcessName\n                    StartTime = $Process.StartTime\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        return @{ Running = $false }\n    } catch {\n        return @{ Running = $false }\n    }\n}","newText":"# Check if service is running\nfunction Test-ServiceRunning {\n    try {\n        # Method 1: Check TCP connection\n        $Connections = Get-NetTCPConnection -LocalPort $Port -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue -State Listen\n        if ($Connections) {\n            $Pid = $Connections[0].OwningProcess\n            if ($Pid -and $Pid -gt 0) {\n                $Process = Get-Process -Id $Pid -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n                if ($Process) {\n                    return @{\n                        Running = $true\n                        Pid = $Pid\n                        ProcessName = $Process.ProcessName\n                        StartTime = $Process.StartTime\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        # Method 2: Fallback - test HTTP endpoint\n        try {\n            $Response = Invoke-WebRequest -Uri \"http://localhost:$Port/health\" -TimeoutSec 3 -UseBasicParsing -ErrorAction Stop\n            if ($Response.StatusCode -eq 200) {\n                return @{ Running = $true; Pid = $null; ProcessName = \"unknown\"; StartTime = $null }\n            }\n        } catch {\n            # HTTP check failed, continue to return not running\n        }\n        \n        return @{ Running = $false }\n    } catch {\n        return @{ Running = $false }\n    }\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":39743,"output":645,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40388,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772682771575}}
