{"type":"message","id":"a3f8e291","parentId":"56f56963","timestamp":"2026-03-05T03:53:32.475Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"服务启动仍然失败。让我检查一下为什么。可能是启动服务的方式有问题，或者环境变量加载有问题。\n\n让我手动测试一下启动服务的逻辑：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我检查服务启动失败的具体原因：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a53c434018154ed9b562ace2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.codex\\cn-bridge\" ; python -c \"import fastapi, uvicorn, httpx, yaml, dotenv; print('Dependencies OK')\"","description":"检查 Python 依赖"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":41228,"output":149,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41377,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772682809463}}
