{"type":"message","id":"6aeb8169","parentId":"69797ab5","timestamp":"2026-03-05T03:54:59.242Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到错误了：`找不到与环境变量\"EnvironmentVariables\"匹配的参数`。这是因为 `Start-Process` 的 `-EnvironmentVariables` 参数在 PowerShell 5.x 中不可用（它是在 PowerShell 7+ 中添加的）。\n\n让我修复这个问题，使用不同的方法来设置环境变量：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"发现 PowerShell 版本兼容问题，让我修复：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_149dd23d40d54252969f3e2d","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"G:\\openClaw\\xiaoxia\\skills\\codex-cn-bridge\\scripts\\watchdog.ps1","oldText":"    # Use Start-Process for better compatibility\n    try {\n        $ProcessArgs = @{\n            FilePath = \"python\"\n            ArgumentList = \"proxy.py\"\n            WorkingDirectory = $ProxyDir\n            WindowStyle = \"Hidden\"\n            PassThru = $true\n        }\n        \n        # Load environment variables from .env file\n        if (Test-Path $EnvFile) {\n            $EnvVars = @{}\n            Get-Content $EnvFile | ForEach-Object {\n                if ($_ -notmatch \"^#\" -and $_ -match \"=\") {\n                    $key, $value = $_.Split(\"=\", 2)\n                    $EnvVars[$key.Trim()] = $value.Trim()\n                }\n            }\n            $ProcessArgs['EnvironmentVariables'] = $EnvVars\n        }\n        \n        Write-Log \"Starting process with args: $ProxyDir\\proxy.py\" \"INFO\"\n        $Process = Start-Process @ProcessArgs\n        \n        Start-Sleep -Seconds 5\n        \n        $Status = Test-ServiceRunning\n        if ($Status.Running) {\n            Write-Log \"$ServiceName service started (PID: $($Status.Pid))\" \"INFO\"\n            return $true\n        } else {\n            Write-Log \"Service start failed - service not detected after 5s\" \"ERROR\"\n            if ($Process) {\n                Write-Log \"Process exited: $($Process.HasExited)\" \"ERROR\"\n            }\n            return $false\n        }\n    } catch {\n        Write-Log \"Error starting service: $_\" \"ERROR\"\n        return $false\n    }","newText":"    # Use ProcessStartInfo for better compatibility\n    try {\n        $StartInfo = New-Object System.Diagnostics.ProcessStartInfo\n        $StartInfo.FileName = \"python\"\n        $StartInfo.Arguments = \"proxy.py\"\n        $StartInfo.WorkingDirectory = $ProxyDir\n        $StartInfo.UseShellExecute = $false\n        $StartInfo.CreateNoWindow = $true\n        $StartInfo.WindowStyle = \"Hidden\"\n        \n        # Copy current environment variables\n        $CurrentEnv = [System.Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariables()\n        foreach ($Key in $CurrentEnv.Keys) {\n            $StartInfo.EnvironmentVariables[$Key] = $CurrentEnv[$Key]\n        }\n        \n        # Load and add environment variables from .env file\n        if (Test-Path $EnvFile) {\n            Get-Content $EnvFile | ForEach-Object {\n                if ($_ -notmatch \"^#\" -and $_ -match \"=\") {\n                    $key, $value = $_.Split(\"=\", 2)\n                    $StartInfo.EnvironmentVariables[$key.Trim()] = $value.Trim()\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        Write-Log \"Starting process with ProcessStartInfo\" \"INFO\"\n        $Process = New-Object System.Diagnostics.Process\n        $Process.StartInfo = $StartInfo\n        $Process.Start() | Out-Null\n        \n        Start-Sleep -Seconds 5\n        \n        $Status = Test-ServiceRunning\n        if ($Status.Running) {\n            Write-Log \"$ServiceName service started (PID: $($Status.Pid))\" \"INFO\"\n            return $true\n        } else {\n            Write-Log \"Service start failed - service not detected after 5s\" \"ERROR\"\n            if ($Process) {\n                Write-Log \"Process exited: $($Process.HasExited)\" \"ERROR\"\n            }\n            return $false\n        }\n    } catch {\n        Write-Log \"Error starting service: $_\" \"ERROR\"\n        return $false\n    }"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":43904,"output":997,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44901,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772682875272}}
